snippet.title: Warframe | The Jackal 2.0, Available Now!
snippet.description: The Deadlock Protocol is available now on all platforms! Get ready to face an upgraded threat: the Jackal 2.0 is equipped with a suite of the latest technology and combat capabilities. Explore a fully remastered Corpus fleet, a new Quest for the tactical Protea Warframe and much more. Plus, take on the upgraded Jackal at Level 100 in 7 days of Jackal Sorties after launch! https://wrfr.me/deadlock
